# std — v1.1 typeclass library

Single-import aggregator for the v1.1 std typeclass library.  Consumers
can write one import and pick what they want by name:

```text
[Monoid, intSum, combineAll, listFunctor, ...](./std/index.ssc)
```

instead of stitching together imports from each individual file
(`semigroup-monoid.ssc`, `functor-applicative-monad.ssc`, etc.).

Transitive imports propagate through all three backends as of step 7,
so loading this file pulls in every typeclass, instance, and helper
the library ships.

[intSum, stringConcat, listConcat, combineAll, combineAllOption](./semigroup-monoid.ssc)

[listMonad, optionMonad, pureList, pureOption, map2List, map2Option, sequenceList, sequenceOption](./functor-applicative-monad.ssc)

[listFoldable, optionFoldable, listTraversable, optionTraversable, foldLeftList, foldLeftOption, foldRightList, foldRightOption, traverseListOption, traverseOptionList](./foldable-traversable.ssc)

[Left, Right, mapRight, flatMapRight, foldEither, isLeft, isRight](./either.ssc)

[listSelective, optionSelective, selectList, selectOption, branchList, branchOption](./selective.ssc)

[optionUnitError, raiseOption, handleOption, attemptOption, raiseEither, handleEither, attemptEither](./monaderror.ssc)

[tupleBifunctor, bimapTuple, leftMapTuple, rightMapTuple, bimapEither, leftMapEither, rightMapEither](./bifunctor.ssc)
